{"parentUuid":"068d5975-9af8-438a-8200-c6145a032eb4","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01Cp63EDMxHdZKQFTuo7p3E6","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"鋭い指摘。**その通り、MCP経由だと意味ない。**\n\n理由：\n\n```\nClaude Code → MCP Server → Gemini CLI → 結果\n                                          ↓\nClaude Code ← MCP Server ← 結果を受け取る\n```\n\n結果を **Claude の context に戻す** ので、Opus のトークンを消費する。入力も出力も課金対象。\n\n**正しい使い分け：**\n\n| 方法 | トークン節約 |\n|------|-------------|\n| Gemini CLI を **直接ターミナルで使う** | **効果あり** — Claude 無関係 |\n| Gemini CLI を **MCP Server 経由で Claude から呼ぶ** | **効果なし** — 結局 Claude が処理する |\n\nつまり：\n\n- **リサーチ・探索** → ターミナルで直接 `gemini` を叩く\n- **結果の要約だけ** → 必要な部分だけ Claude に貼る\n- **コード編集** → Claude が直接やる\n\nMCP で繋ぐのはトークンロンダリングにしかならない。直接使い分けるのが正解。"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":322,"cache_read_input_tokens":20279,"output_tokens":542,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":322,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZkLDs7XbCFfKdp3Pms9y","type":"assistant","uuid":"f8172cea-ab31-4d7a-b338-1638d8dd4b3f","timestamp":"2026-04-05T08:46:33.663Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/ryota","sessionId":"4193835a-47c3-46ea-936c-e8950aa1aad2","version":"2.1.89","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
